In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started on February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. A total of 8 teams have been divided into two groups. In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started on February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. A total of 8 teams have been divided into two groups. The first group includes India, Pakistan, New Zealand and Bangladesh. At the same time, the second group includes teams from South Africa, Afghanistan, Australia and England. The final match of the tournament will be held on March 9. The Indian team has won its first match against Bangladesh by 6 wickets. The great match between India and Pakistan will be played in Dubai on February 23. After this, the Indian team will play the third and last match of the group stage against New Zealand on March 2. The top-2 teams of both the groups will qualify for the semi-finals. But before the challenge of Pakistan, the Indian cricket team has made a good start as soon as it won over the Bangladesh cricket team. After this victory, a wave of happiness also ran among the Indian cricket fans. What did the Indian fans say after Bangladesh's defeat? How eager are Indian fans for the upcoming India vs Pakistan match? Why are Indian cricket fans issuing warnings to Pakistan cricket team? Why do Bangladesh cricket team fans now want to defeat Pakistan cricket team? Why are Bangladeshi fans angry with their captain Nazmul Hossain Shanto? To know this, watch this special video of Zee Switch's Chayan Rastogi directly from Dubai International Cricket Stadium, where he is talking to Bangladeshi cricket fans and Indian cricket fans.

Shami, Arshdeep Singh, Ravindra Jadeja, Varun Chakaravarthy.

Non Travelling substitutes: Yashasvi Jaiswal, Mohammed Siraj and Shivam Dube.

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS Real Madrid 3-1 Man City | Mbappe (3) & Nico Goals
snippet.description:
Manchester City were knocked out this season‚Äôs UEFA Champions League after a 6-3 aggregate defeat to Real Madrid.
Pep Guardiola‚Äôs side were beaten 3-1 in the second leg at the Santiago Bernabeu with Kylian Mbappe scoring a hat-trick for the current European champions.

After a 3-2 defeat in the first leg at the Etihad, City fell further behind in the tie when the Frenchman scored the opener after just four minutes.

And we suffered a further early early setback with John Stones going off injured after just eight minutes while Erling Haaland was unable to feature in the fixture.

Mbappe scored two more either side of half-time before Nico scored his first goal for City in the dying minutes.

In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started on February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. A total of 8 teams have been divided into two groups. The first group includes India, Pakistan, New Zealand and Bangladesh. At the same time, the second group includes teams from South Africa, Afghanistan, Australia and England. The final match of the tournament will be held on March 9. The Indian team has won its first match against Bangladesh by 6 wickets. The great match between India and Pakistan will be played in Dubai on February 23. After this, the Indian team will play the third and last match of the group stage against New Zealand on March 2. The top-2 teams of both the groups will qualify for the semi-finals. Why do Bangladesh cricket team fans now want to defeat Pakistan cricket team? Why are Bangladeshi fans angry with their captain Nazmul Hossain Shanto? How did Indian cricket fans roast Bangladeshi fans and Pakistan cricket fans? To know more, watch this special video of Zee Switch's Chayan Rastogi directly from Dubai International Cricket Stadium, where he is talking to Bangladeshi cricket fans and Indian cricket fans.

Shami, Arshdeep Singh, Ravindra Jadeja, Varun Chakaravarthy.

Non Travelling substitutes: Yashasvi Jaiswal, Mohammed Siraj and Shivam Dube.

snippet.title: KABULI PULAO | Afghani Biryani Style Rice | Afghanistan Special Recipe Cooking In Indian Village
snippet.description:
In this video, we bring the delicious and traditional Kabuli Pulao, a special rice dish from Afghanistan, cooked in our Indian village style. This flavorful pulao is made with fragrant basmati rice, tender meat, sweet carrots, and raisins, giving it a perfect balance of sweetness and spices.

Watch as we prepare this Afghani biryani-style rice using natural village cooking methods over a firewood stove. This is a must-try recipe for all pulao and biryani lovers!

We follow our traditional village cooking style using fresh ingredients and firewood. The result is an authentic, mouthwatering dish that you can easily try at home!

snippet.title: Ek Badnaam Aashram Season 3 PT 2 - Official Trailer | Bobby Deol, Aaditi Pohankar | Amazon MX Player
snippet.description:
Amazon MX Player presents

In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started on February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. A total of 8 teams have been divided into two groups. The first group includes India, Pakistan, New Zealand and Bangladesh. At the same time, the second group includes teams from South Africa, Afghanistan, Australia and England. The final match of the tournament will be held on March 9. The Indian team has won its first match against Bangladesh by 6 wickets. The great match between India and Pakistan will be played in Dubai on February 23. After this, the Indian team will play the third and last match of the group stage against New Zealand on March 2. The top-2 teams of both the groups will qualify for the semi-finals. But before the challenge of Pakistan, the Indian cricket team has made a good start as soon as it won over the Bangladesh cricket team. After this victory, a wave of happiness also ran among the Indian cricket fans. What did the Indian fans say after Bangladesh's defeat? How eager are Indian fans for the upcoming India vs Pakistan match? Why are Indian cricket fans issuing warnings to Pakistan cricket team? Why do Bangladesh cricket team fans now want to defeat Pakistan cricket team? Why are Bangladeshi fans angry with their captain Nazmul Hossain Shanto? To know this, watch this special video of Zee Switch's Chayan Rastogi directly from Dubai International Cricket Stadium, where he is talking to Bangladeshi cricket fans and Indian cricket fans.


India‚Äôs squad for ICC Champions Trophy, 2025: Rohit Sharma (Captain), Shubman Gill (Vice-captain), Virat Kohli, Shreyas Iyer, KL Rahul (WK), Rishabh Pant (WK), Hardik Pandya, Axar Patel, Washington Sundar, Kuldeep Yadav, Harshit Rana, Mohd. Shami, Arshdeep Singh, Ravindra Jadeja, Varun Chakaravarthy.

Non Travelling substitutes: Yashasvi Jaiswal, Mohammed Siraj and Shivam Dube.

In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started on February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. A total of 8 teams have been divided into two groups. The first group includes India, Pakistan, New Zealand and Bangladesh. At the same time, the second group includes teams from South Africa, Afghanistan, Australia and England. The final match of the tournament will be held on March 9. The Indian team has won its first match against Bangladesh by 6 wickets. The great match between India and Pakistan will be played in Dubai on February 23. After this, the Indian team will play the third and last match of the group stage against New Zealand on March 2. The top-2 teams of both the groups will qualify for the semi-finals. But before the challenge of Pakistan, the Indian cricket team has made a good start as soon as it won over the Bangladesh cricket team. After this victory, a wave of happiness also ran among the Indian cricket fans. What did the Indian fans say after Bangladesh's defeat? How eager are Indian fans for the upcoming India vs Pakistan match? Why are Indian cricket fans issuing warnings to Pakistan cricket team? Why do Bangladesh cricket team fans now want to defeat Pakistan cricket team? Why are Bangladeshi fans angry with their captain Nazmul Hossain Shanto? To know this, watch this special video of Zee Switch's Chayan Rastogi directly from Dubai International Cricket Stadium, where he is talking to Bangladeshi cricket fans and Indian cricket fans.

Shami, Arshdeep Singh, Ravindra Jadeja, Varun Chakaravarthy.

Non Travelling substitutes: Yashasvi Jaiswal, Mohammed Siraj and Shivam Dube.

In the ICC Champions Trophy 2025, India will play all its matches in Dubai while Pakistan will host the rest of the countries. The tournament has started on February 19 and the Indian team has started its campaign from February 20. A total of 8 teams have been divided into two groups. The first group includes India, Pakistan, New Zealand and Bangladesh. At the same time, the second group includes teams from South Africa, Afghanistan, Australia and England. The final match of the tournament will be held on March 9. The Indian team has won its first match against Bangladesh by 6 wickets. The great match between India and Pakistan will be played in Dubai on February 23. After this, the Indian team will play the third and last match of the group stage against New Zealand on March 2. The top-2 teams of both the groups will qualify for the semi-finals. But before the challenge of Pakistan, the Indian cricket team has made a good start as soon as it won over the Bangladesh cricket team. ‚úîÔ∏è Sharing needles or syringes
‚úîÔ∏è From mother to child (during pregnancy, childbirth, or breastfeeding)
‚úîÔ∏è Blood transfusions (though rare due to screening)

Prime Video India Presents
Suzhal ‚Äì The Vortex Season 2 Official Trailer

About:
Created by Pushkar and Gayatri, Suzhal - The Vortex S2 begins with the shocking murder of senior activist lawyer Chellapa, who defended Nandini. Sakkarai is summoned to assist the family in their time of crisis. Set against the backdrop of the massive Ashtakaali Festival, the case unravels family secrets and betrayals, and acts in the past that cast long shadows on the present.

snippet.title: Na Kajre Ki Dhaar [4k Song] | Suniel Shetty, Poonam Jhaver | Mohra (1994) | Popular Romantic Songs
snippet.description:
Stay updated with the latest videos from Shemaroo Filmi Gaane Subscribe on the below link.
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCP6uH_XlsxrXwZQ4DlqbqPg

"Na Kajre Ki Dhaar", is from the classic Bollywood movie Mohra (1994). It is one of the most iconic and memorable songs from the 90s. The song is beautifully composed by Viju Shah and sung by Sadhana Sargam and Pankaj Udhas. The lyrics were written by Indeevar. It features Poonam Jhaver and Suniel Shetty in a romantic dance sequence that became quite popular due to its catchy rhythm and the intense chemistry between the lead actors.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
